1、切换到master分支，git pull 然后直接上传

git checkout master
git pull
git add
git commit
git push origin master



2、切换到drv_only分支，git merge --no-ff origin/master，然后push上传

git checkout drv_only
git pull
git merge --no-ff origin/master
git push origin drv_only



3、切换到dev分支，git merge --no-ff origin/drv_only，然后push上传

git checkout dev
git pull
git merge --no-ff origin/drv_only
git push origin dev



ps: git merge --no-ff origin/的分支是前一个分支




--------------- modem --------------------
git checkout dev
git pull
git merge --no-ff origin/master
git push origin dev






!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!需要注意 ProjectConfig.mk 文件中有没有修改
